data.title: U.S. soldiers conduct a dismounted patrol through the northeastern section of the city of Tarmiyah, Iraq, March 13, 2009. The soldiers are assigned to Company C, 1st Battalion, 111th Infantry Regiment
data.text: U.S. soldiers conduct a dismounted patrol through the northeastern section of the city of Tarmiyah, Iraq, March 13, 2009. The soldiers are assigned to Company C, 1st Battalion, 111th Infantry Regiment, 56th Stryker Brigade Combat Team, 28th Infantry Division, Pennsylvania National Guard, Multinational Division Baghdad.
